580
00:41:40,045 --> 00:41:41,345
- Uľavilo sa?
- To hej.

581
00:41:41,446 --> 00:41:42,380
Čo?

582
00:41:42,481 --> 00:41:43,782
Kretén jeden.

583
00:41:58,630 --> 00:42:00,031
Tak už otváraj, idiot.

584
00:42:38,103 --> 00:42:39,270
Nie je tu.

585
00:42:40,906 --> 00:42:43,174
